# Consent toggles
consent-Example-name = Example Consent Toggle
consent-Example-desc = This is just here as an example for how to add consent toggles.

consent-NonconAggressor = Non-Con Aggressor
    .desc = Mark yourself as a potential Non-Con aggressor. Combined with the Non-Con icon toggle, you will display a RED marker with horns pointing UP to other opted-in players. If you also enable Non-Con Victim, the marker becomes PURPLE with horns at both top and bottom (either role).

consent-NonconVictim = Non-Con Victim
    .desc = Mark yourself as a potential Non-Con victim. Combined with the Non-Con icon toggle, you will display a BLUE marker with horns pointing DOWN to other opted-in players. If you also enable Non-Con Aggressor, the marker becomes PURPLE with horns at both top and bottom (either role).